Inside the Chivtron base, a long beeping sounds rings off. A 
nano-cycle later, the door of a CR chamber opens up and reveals 
a female bot. Her wounds were healed by now and she seemed 100% ready.

Starstomp: Now where the heck are Windlord and the rest?

She walks towards the control room in hopes of meeting someone on the 
way. She wonders also if the attacks have been thwarted or if those 
jerks were still outside. Maybe they had dug the hole and fled from 
the base, which she hoped they did...
